Stomach Disease, including Acid Reflux Disease
Gallbladder and Biliary Disease, including Pancreas
Small Intestine Disease
Anorectal Disorders, including Hemorrhoid Disease
Skin Cancers and Skin Lesions
Benign Breast Disease
Dr. Zbinden is Board Certified in General Surgery and is a Fellow of the American College of Surgeons. He is a current member of both the North Carolina Medical Society and the Mecklenburg County Medical Society. He is also on the teaching faculty at Carolinas Medical Center. He serves as a Trauma Surgeon for CMC Hospital and operates in both the CMC and Presbyterian hospital systems.
Dr. Zbinden sees patients at our Pineville and Mercy Medical Plaza offices and welcomes all new patients in the Charlotte area and surrounding communities.', N'')
